%% Diagram: Font swap with metric overrides — eliminating font-induced CLS
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant N as Network
    participant L as Layout

    Note over B: Without metric overrides
    U->>B: Navigate
    B->>L: Render with Arial fallback
    L-->>U: Visible text (Arial metrics)
    B->>N: Fetch web font
    N-->>B: Inter.woff2 arrives
    B->>L: Reflow with Inter metrics
    L-->>U: Layout shift! (CLS spike)

    Note over B: With size-adjust + ascent-override
    U->>B: Navigate
    B->>L: Render Arial sized to match Inter
    L-->>U: Visible text (Inter dimensions)
    B->>N: Fetch web font
    N-->>B: Inter.woff2 arrives
    B->>L: Swap glyphs, identical metrics
    L-->>U: No layout shift (CLS = 0)
